displayName: Altar of the Demon of Regeneration, Jien

parameters:
Voice Priestess Phoni: For someone like me who has lived as
a priestess, this place seems to be too stimulating.

Explorer Armada: What on earth is this place... Is this the
altar of the Djinn as written in the ruins?
Explorer Armada: First of all, is this Varie...?

Mage Relm: I don't know... What I can say for certain is
that this place is enveloped in tremendous magical power.

Mage Relm: I don't understand the principles or methods at
all. This place might be different from the previous ruins
in terms of its nature.
Priestess Sophia: Are you okay, Nora-chan?

Thief Nora: I can see through this... There are dead bodies
inside!

Priestess Sophia: I wonder when these corpses are from...
They seem to have stopped decaying... It's eerie.

Priestess Phoni: Y-Yes... I'm starting to get scared now...
This place is beyond human understanding... It has surpassed
our understanding.

Priestess Phoni: For someone like me who has lived as a
priestess, this place seems to be incredibly stimulating.

Clea: Please wait here. Armada-san and I will proceed
further inside.
Noble Ect: Looks like we were defeated by a monster.
Explorer Armada: Ugh, I have to help Clea and the others...!
Noble Ect: No need to worry.

Noble Ect: Please make sure to rescue the girls who have
collapsed inside.

Noble Ect: Now that there's no need to worry, come with me
to the mansion and let's talk about various things.

Noble Ect: The situation hasn't changed. Rather, I'm
grateful that you defeated the monster.

Explorer Armada: Cut it out, Ect! This isn't like you at
all!

Explorer Armada: Where did you go, Ect, my senior who
dreamed of archaeology together with me!?

Noble Ect: I died on the day of that cave-in accident! My
dreams, our relationship, you must know about them too--

Mage Relm: This is not the time for doing something like
this! This space might collapse, hurry to the magic circle!

Noble Ect: Collapse...!? I won't allow such a thing! This
place is the hope of Valier!

Noble Ect: If this place disappears... Valier, Valier will
truly be dead!

Leader of the Chronos Thieves, Gift: Master, I'm sorry, but
I'll escape first.
Clea: Are you okay? Are you injured!?

Voice Priestess Phoni: I'm fine. Let's escape from here
quickly!

Explorer Armada: Things are getting even more dangerous...
Now, everyone, let's move to the magic circle quickly!

Noble Ect: Ugh, my legs... damn it, I'm doing this for
Valier, ugh...

Noble Ect: Am I going to die like my father... all alone...
miserably... ugh... damn it!
Explorer Armada: Men shouldn't be crying like that.

Noble Ect: You idiot! Hurry up and run, there's no need for
us to die together!

Explorer Armada: You're doing great. It's been a while since
I last saw the Ect I know.

Explorer Armada: Alright, let me lend you a shoulder this
time. I'll be the one to help you out.
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)
Adventurer Armada: Can you read the stone tablet for me?

Mage Relm: Understood... It seems to be a continuation of
what was written on the floor of the previous ruins.

Mage Relm: The accursed goddesses... the wielders of the
small sun of Sol that brings destruction.

Mage Relm: We have already been destroyed. The passage of
time will eventually take away our bodies and souls.
Adventurer Armada: So this is their tomb, huh?

Mage Relm: Please wait, there is still more... We will not
give up completely, we have decided to wait.

Mage Relm: When the goddesses leave the earth and the small
sun disappears, the time will come when those who obstruct
us will completely vanish.

Mage Relm: At the end of the seemingly endless years...
someone with the intellect and abilities to gather the four
keys will appear.

Mage Relm: To fulfill the eternal desire of returning to
this world with their lives, to achieve the dream... of
eternal return.
Adventurer Armada: Does this mean... we are sacrifices?
Voice Priestess Phoni: Kyaa! P-Please let go!

Noble Orikuto: Amazing...! This is the Devil's Ruins... It
really did exist!

Adventurer Armada: What do you think you're doing, Orikuto!
Release Phoni, my comrade, right now!

Noble Orikuto: I don't mean to hinder you, but you haven't
realized the importance of this ruins.

Noble Orikuto: The Devil's Ruins... This should bring many
researchers and mages to Valier once again!

Noble Orikuto: You should understand too, something that
will replace the Crystal Mines is necessary for Valier!

Noble Orikuto: Naturally, we will sell the rights to
investigate this place to the Magic Academy. You should also
participate in the research and investigation.

Adventurer Armada: Even if this place could replace the
Crystal Mines, it's not what Valier truly needs.

Adventurer Armada: Our ancestors called themselves
'pioneers'. What Valier truly needs is a strong heart to
carve out our own destiny!

Adventurer Armada: It is important for each and every person
living in Valier to seize their own destiny, rather than
having it handed to them.

Adventurer Armada: That's why we're all children of
pioneers, you know!?

Noble Orikuto: I understand your thoughts. I will use any
means necessary to carve out my own destiny.

Noble Orikuto: I hope you make a wise decision regarding the
hostage we have here.

Adventurer Armada: Hmph, there's no need to think about it.
This place belongs to you, so release Phoni immediately.

Noble Orikuto: If you leave here and the Chronos Bandit
Corps reinforcements arrive, that's what will happen--
Noble Orikuto: What is this... What is this?!

Mage Relm: The magic spell formation is expanding at an
incredible speed! Please be careful... Something's wrong,
definitely wrong!
Thief Nora: M-my body... feels... heavy... ugh

Priestess Sophia: Ah... It feels like my energy is being
drained...

Clea: ...Relm-san, if we defeat this person, will the
problem be resolved?

Mage Relm: I think the phenomenon of having our energy
drained... will stop happening... if we can win, that is.

Clea: Armada-san! We'll handle this somehow, please take
care of that side!

Adventurer Armada: I've been entrusted with this! I will
definitely protect Phoni.

Voice Priestess Phoni: I'm okay! Clea-san, please focus on
the battle!
Clea: I apologize for waking up from a long sleep.
Clea: I will go back to sleep right away!

events.name: デバッグ用（削除しないこと
強く儚いものたち並列実行
